## Standards

- Derive every resource name from `local.name_prefix`; never hardcode names.
- Merge `local.default_tags` into every taggable resource (`var.tags` is for
  stack-specific additions).
- Constrain new variables with `validation` blocks â€” invariants live in the
  code, not in tribal knowledge.
